#!/bin/bash

cat << 'WELCOME'
╔═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║                          Welcome to CrowOS                                ║
║                    Rescue & Recovery Live Environment                     ║
╚═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

QUICK START GUIDE
─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

ESSENTIAL KEYBINDINGS (Mod = Windows/Super Key)
  Mod+Enter           Open new terminal
  Mod+d               Launch application (dmenu)
  Mod+Shift+q         Close window
  Mod+Shift+e         Exit i3

WINDOW MANAGEMENT
  Mod+Shift+Space     Toggle floating/tiling mode
  Mod+f               Toggle fullscreen
  Mod+h               Split horizontally
  Mod+v               Split vertically
  
  Mouse Controls (using modifier key):
  - Mod+Left-drag     Move floating window
  - Mod+Right-drag    Resize floating window
  - Drag borders      Resize tiled windows

NAVIGATION
  Mod+Arrow Keys      Move focus between windows
  Mod+1 through 0     Switch to workspace 1-10
  Mod+Shift+1-0       Move window to workspace

LAYOUTS
  Mod+s               Stacking layout
  Mod+w               Tabbed layout
  Mod+e               Toggle split layout

USEFUL COMMANDS
  lsblk               List all drives and partitions
  fdisk -l            Detailed disk information
  ip addr             Show network interfaces
  tree                Directory tree view
  htop                Process monitor

Press Enter to close this window...
WELCOME

read
